name: Murgulis
text:
It radiates the ungovernable rage of a fearless champion—and the slight smell of fish.

Purchasable when available in the shop.

name: Sweetheart
text:
Put your heart into the game, and victory’s the sweetest!

Acquired by winning 5 games in ranked mode, February 2025.

name: Blighted Souls
text:
All they are is drust in the wind.

Acquired by winning 5 games in ranked mode, January 2025.
